    • Method Detail

      • authenticated

        void authenticated(FirebaseSimpleLoginError error,
                 FirebaseSimpleLoginUser user)
        Method called when handler is invoked. If error is not null, check for error status. If user is null, no user is logged in. If user is not null, there is a logged in user.
        Parameters:
        error - FirebaseSimpleLoginError for callback; will be null if no error.
        user - The returned User object.
